So at this point, if you downloaded the EDAR package, you can load it.

00:11:51.000 --> 00:11:54.000
And you'll see that, you know, the storms data sets in there.

00:11:54.000 --> 00:11:56.000
The cases data sets in there.

00:11:56.000 --> 00:11:58.000
Actually, all the data sets on that cheat sheet are in there.

00:11:58.000 --> 00:12:00.000
And all the data sets will go over today.

