And so if I took the code here, I can run an R and verify.

00:12:04.000 --> 00:12:07.000
If I took the code here, I can run an R and verify.

00:12:07.000 --> 00:12:09.000
That gather comes from tidy.

00:12:12.000 --> 00:12:14.000
That's a tidy R library.

00:12:15.000 --> 00:12:22.000
Now you can see that we're going from our rectangular data frame, you know, our table, to our tidy data frame here.

